{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ebfe4e7b57","title":"中共中央关于印发林彪讲话的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"13d84ece2c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":24,"articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第25册 “文化大革命”参考资料 上册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2d2d962f7e","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的、光荣的、正确的中国共产党万岁！光焰无际的、战无不胜的毛泽东思想万岁！我们的伟大领袖毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁","index":0,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7acc15eed8","type":"paragraph","text":"（原载1967年4月21日《人民日报》）中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文化革命小组","index":1,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00d1ba90d5","type":"paragraph","text":"通知","index":2,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25ec08c500","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月二十日）","index":3,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fbabe7876","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，有少数学生和群众又开始到北京和其他地区进行串连，北京的一些学校又派人到外地串连。因此，中央重中停止全国大串连的决定，各地已经外出串连的，应当立即返回。对文化大革命中发生的问题，应当尽量在本地区、本部门、本单位解决，以免影响本地区、本部门、本单位的运动和生产","index":4,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e5b7dbd4c","type":"paragraph","text":"这一通知可以在城乡张贴。","index":5,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d26e8eac6e","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央关于印发林彪讲话的批语","index":6,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5203495997","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月二十四日）","index":7,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3af6cba8f6","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志三月二十日的讲话，很好。这个讲话，高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，提出了当前无产阶级文化大革命运动中的根本问题，不仅对于军队的支左、支工、支农、军管、军训的战斗任务，而且对于开展对党内最大的一小最走资本主义道路当权派的大批判，彻底粉碎资产阶级反动路线，都有重要的指导意义。现印成小册子，发给觉、政、军、民的基层，作为学习文件。","index":8,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea9acf2d01","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央关于福建问题的意见（节录）","index":9,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0da2a4236a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月三十日）五、各革命群众组织之间，有些不同意见，是正常现象。中央认为，遇到这种场合，应","index":10,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"ebfe4e7b57","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":460,"end":460}}}},"__N_SSG":true}